title: The 404 Show 1365 BTTF interviews YouTube Red vampire power Star Wars reactions
text:
The 404 Show 1,365: BTTF interviews, YouTube Red, vampire power, Star Wars reactions 
Cnet Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Today the guys fan out about Jeff's interview with Back to the Future writer Bob Gale and composer Alan Silvestri. They'll also discuss the new ad-free YouTube Red subscription, Fossil's entry into the smartwatch space, how much money you're wasting on vampire power and their reactions to the new Star Wars trailer....
